============== -*- outline -*- ==============

		ULCB/KF sound test

2023/04/12	Kuninori Morimoto <kuninori.morimoto.gx@renesas.com>
=============================================

* Prepare

	Connect ULCB and KF sound input/output like below.
	You need to use headphone branch cable.

	+-ulcb--+
	|(i) (o)|
	+-------+
	+-kf----+
	|( ) ( )|
	|( ) (o)|
	+-------+

* Test

	If your kernel / DT was
		ulcb-simple-audio-card.dtsi
		ulcb-audio-graph-card.dtsi
		ulcb-audio-graph-card2.dtsi
	then
		run ALL-test-2ch+8ch.sh

	If your kernel / DT was
		ulcb-simple-audio-card-mix+split.dtsi
		ulcb-audio-graph-card-mix+split.dtsi
		ulcb-audio-graph-card2-mix+split.dtsi
	then
		run ALL-test-mix+split.sh
